. This critical overview, which contains an extensive bibliography and a filmography, will appeal to students of Film Studies, French Studies, and enthusiasts.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aRealism in motion pictures. 4aFilm and Media Studies 2019. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aAndré Bazin.  aCahiers du cinema.  aComédies et proverbs.  aContes des quatre saisons.  aContes moraux.  aEric Rohmer.  aFrench language.  acostume films.  aediting trait.  aontological realism.  ascreenplay.1 aSchilling, Derek, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152614135440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526141354423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526141354/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles